# parking-management-program
This is a java based project which is used for management of Parking slots. 

This program can be used for management of parking spaces available for the company. It has features like parking slot allocation, vehicle entry and parking slot recommendation, Displaying grid of the parking area. The program also keeps logs of the vehicles entered and exited along with the timestamp.

To run the program,
1.) javac PM.java
2.) java PM

Do as per the program suggests. There are options like Enter a new vehicle, 
Exit a vehicle, View Parking grid, Display logs, Exit. Note that for proper functioning of program, the program should only be exited by the exit option available.
